 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來西歐黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad85cf39f4ea2118bd59d9c3ad2885ba6c0a612b","tid":1292037,"uid":43556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"95291814b5c19a2d7afaddb2931c57e042278aec","tid":1292037,"uid":224095,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dcd5601e3a7dc53b71799b10a1c15526a5e775e1","tid":1292037,"uid":43556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170907/s00001/1504796366706/%E5%93%AA%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E3%80%8A%E8%A1%9B%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%8B-%E5%BE%88%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170907%2Fs00001%2F1504796366706%2F%25E5%2593%25AA%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E3%2580%258B-%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakc70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=01b06f4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170907%2Fs00001%2F1504796366706%2F%25E5%2593%25AA%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E3%2580%258B-%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&h=3ea75ca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170907/s00001/1504796366706/%E5%93%AA%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E3%80%8A%E8%A1%9B%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%8B-%E5%BE%88%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n香港近年有愈來愈示威和遊行，各式各樣都有。英國《衛報》報道，香港可能是全球最多示威的城市，單在2016年，就有近1.2萬宗已向警方申請的公眾集會及逾1300宗遊行紀錄，形容香港「掙扎着從北京手中維護自治權」。<br />\n<br />\n報道以「哪個城市最多示威？」（Which city has the most protests?）為題，引述意大利比薩高等師範學校（Scuala Normala Superiore）人類與社會科學學院教授貝達（Donatella della Porta）表示，全球各地示威數字都有明顯上升趨勢，當中似乎以右翼示威較多。<br />\n<br />\n《衛報》向世界各地警察及相關部門查詢，在有回覆查詢的城市中，香港很可能是全球最多示威的地方。警方數字顯示，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2016年香港有11854次公眾集會及1304次遊行，即平均每日有逾32次集會及超過3.5次遊行。</span></span></strong>不過報道指出，在香港，所有多於50人的集會及多於30人的遊行均需申請，故無法確定當中有多少是真正的示威，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但集會及遊行總數由2015年的6029次，大增超過一倍至2016年的合共13158次，如此大的升幅，「似乎顯示當中很多都是有關政治的示威」。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n至於全球第二多示威城市，相信是墨西哥首都墨西哥城。當地保安部門指，2016年有7011場示威，較2014年9111場少，當中很多都與政治有關。而在歐洲，去年有約5000場示威的德國柏林就成為「示威之都」，連同2016年頭9個月有1983場示威的西班牙首都馬德里，及去年全年有1134場示威的希臘首都雅典，三地大部分示威都與反緊縮（anti-austerity）政策有關。<br />\n<br />\n除香港外，《衛報》指出包括柏林、巴黎及墨西哥城在內的多個城市，要示威均預申請許可。其他地方如荷蘭首都阿姆斯特丹，「搞手」只需通知當局，「不為示威作登記，本身都可以是一種示威方式」。<br />\n<br />\n（衛報）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">溫故而知新，當然示威係包括的士佬反Uber，基層爭取各種社會福利<br />\n但示威，遊行已經成為香港新常態</span></strong></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"一日三次遊行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點bump到咁大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/09_statistics/poes.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F09_statistics%2Fpoes.html&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakc70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=e562df18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/09_statistics/poes.html</a><br />\n警方有公衆活動統計數字<br />\n年份2018<br />\n公衆集會10783<br />\n公衆遊行 1097<br />\n總數 11880"},{"pid":"0eb2ebb2c10320e3c39492c66b4f80608525ae9a","tid":1292037,"uid":43556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"f318c849d42beb920f7895d6cb7f41b84396d8d6","tid":1292037,"uid":100908,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"95291814b5c19a2d7afaddb2931c57e042278aec","tid":1292037,"uid":224095,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dcd5601e3a7dc53b71799b10a1c15526a5e775e1","tid":1292037,"uid":43556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170907/s00001/1504796366706/%E5%93%AA%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E3%80%8A%E8%A1%9B%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%8B-%E5%BE%88%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170907%2Fs00001%2F1504796366706%2F%25E5%2593%25AA%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E3%2580%258B-%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakc70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=01b06f4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170907%2Fs00001%2F1504796366706%2F%25E5%2593%25AA%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E3%2580%258B-%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&h=3ea75ca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170907/s00001/1504796366706/%E5%93%AA%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8